00:38:47,710 --> 00:38:48,630
Let's set aside the fact

851
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:50,760
whether this is a subject I like or not.

852
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:52,840
Even this doctorate

853
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,280
was my mom's wish.

854
00:38:57,070 --> 00:38:58,710
I don't know much

855
00:38:59,030 --> 00:39:00,230
about artificial intelligence.

856
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,000
But I know you.

857
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,230
When we were kids,

858
00:39:03,230 --> 00:39:04,960
you would skip meals and sleep

859
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:07,110
just to solve

860
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,550
a bonus question.

861
00:39:09,230 --> 00:39:11,320
Everyone thought you were a nerd.

862
00:39:11,630 --> 00:39:12,440
But when I looked at you,

863
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,840
I thought you were awesome.

864
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:16,630
That's why you should stand firm now.

865
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:20,150
On both your studies and relationship.

866
00:39:21,550 --> 00:39:22,190
Hold up.

867
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:24,710
Aren't you here to look up on Ding Ye?

868
00:39:24,710 --> 00:39:26,150
Why are you talking about relationships?

869
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,320
You have a bracelet

870
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,190
that's for Fang Mingyu, don't you?

871
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:34,400
How did you know about the bracelet?

872
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:35,590
Your roommate

873
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:37,040
mistook me for Fang Mingyu.

874
00:39:39,190 --> 00:39:40,400
That blabbermouth.

875
00:39:41,070 --> 00:39:43,230
I prepared that gift a long time ago.

876
00:39:43,230 --> 00:39:44,480
It's out of fashion now.

877
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:45,510
I can't give it to her anymore.

878
00:39:45,510 --> 00:39:46,960
It doesn't matter
if it's out of fashion.

879
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,280
What matters most

880
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,510
is whether or not

881
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:51,360
you still have feelings for her.

882
00:39:52,230 --> 00:39:53,280
If you don't,

883
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,840
why do you still have that bracelet?

884
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:57,320
I didn't get a chance to toss it out.

885
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:58,880
Then why are you still single?

886
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,590
It's hard to date as a PhD student.

887
00:40:01,670 --> 00:40:02,550
Fine.

888
00:40:02,550 --> 00:40:04,150
You always have a comeback.

889
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:06,320
Then tell me.

890
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:08,400
If Fang Mingyu tells you today

891
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,280
that she is getting married,

892
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:10,400
won't you have any regrets?

893
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:22,360
Fine, Yingzi.

894
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:23,990
I can't hide anything from you.

895
00:40:26,190 --> 00:40:27,840
Aren't we always like this?

896
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:29,000
When we were kids,

897
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,230
you could always tell

898
00:40:30,230 --> 00:40:32,070
what was on my mind.

899
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:39,630
Here's your 7 Up.

900
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:57,440
Thanks.

901
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,880
Yingzi, that's my soda.

902
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:05,590
Sorry.

903
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:07,480
I'll get you another bottle later.

904
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,510
That's not what I meant.

905
00:41:08,510 --> 00:41:09,190
I...

906
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:18,000
Are you done?

907
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:19,480
If you are, we should go home.

908
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:20,630
I'm not quite done yet.

909
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:21,590
You guys go ahead.

910
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:25,360
I'll go with you.

911
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:26,670
Zhuang Yuan isn't done either.

912
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:39,920
We'll get going, then.

913
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:41,400
Bye-bye.

914
00:41:55,150 --> 00:41:56,480
I'm stuffed.

915
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:57,400
You can finish it.

916
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:03,670
Why are you sitting over there?

917
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:06,840
Mencius once said,

918
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,590
"Men and women are to remain separated."

919
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:09,630
What are you...

920
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:10,960
It's also stated in the "Book of Rites".

921
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:12,360
"Men and women are different."

922
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,360
What are you trying to say?

923
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:15,110
Yingzi.

924
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:18,030
I have someone I like.

925
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:19,760
So?

926
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:27,590
You don't think I like you, do you?

927
00:42:28,070 --> 00:42:29,110
Don't you?

928
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:30,480
When we played Truth or Dare
the other day,

929
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:31,320
you said it yourself.

930
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:31,760
Yuck!

931
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:32,800
Who gave you that confidence?

932
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:34,440
I wasn't being serious, okay?

933
00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:35,360
Then why have you been

934
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,670
going home with me
after school these days?

935
00:42:36,670 --> 00:42:37,070
Yuck!

936
00:42:37,070 --> 00:42:38,150
Who wants to go home with you?

937
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,190
I just want to copy your homework.

938
00:42:39,190 --> 00:42:40,360
And the day we were watching
"Chinese Paladin".

939
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:41,670
Why did you sit behind me on my bike?

940
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:43,150
Yuck! Who wants to sit behind you?

941
00:42:43,150 --> 00:42:44,150
Everyone else was taken.

942
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:45,070
I had no choice.

943
00:42:45,070 --> 00:42:45,760
Are you saying

944
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:46,880
that you wanted
to ride behind someone else?

945
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:47,760
Anyone but you.

946
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:48,630
Was it Guan Chao?

947
00:42:48,630 --> 00:42:49,840
Yuck! There's no way I'd pick him!

948
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,670
Then who was it?

949
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:51,630
It was Jiang...
